  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Main
    The controller class
    Mediator
    Class to convert String sentence into CoreMap Class sentence.
    Models
    Class to load Models of stanford coreNLP and Apache OpenNLP
    NLP
    Class from where all modules are loaded and NLP pipeline starts.
    NLPApi
    Class defining the seperate APIs
    NLPDeepParsing
    Class to do stanford dependency parsing.
    NLPLemmatizer
    A Class to do stemming on a words.
    NLPNamedEntityGateAnnie
    A Class to find Named Entity using GATE ANNIE.
    NLPNamedEntityOpenNLP
    A Class to find Named Entity using Apache OpenNLP.
    NLPNamedEntityStanford
    A Class to find Named Entity using Stanford NER.
    NLPPartOfSpeech
    A Class to get part of speech of a sentence.
    NLPSentenceSplitter
    A Class to split pargraph into sentences using Apache OpenNLP
    NLPShallowParsing
    Class to do stanford tree parsing/ shallow parsing.
    NLPTokenizer
    A Class to create tokens of a sentence.
